You know, as an afterthought, if I were an innocent bystander and heard a 
comment like this, my first question to him would be &quot;Why is it called 
Frank&#39;s Box and not Christopher&#39;s Box, and is Frank giving lessons?&quot;

Even if he called it a &quot;ghost box,&quot; there&#39;s an awful lot of people out 
there who know of it as Frank&#39;s Box.

Maybe I&#39;m too logical in a world gone mad.

Zack

